<mxCell id="legend-content" value="✓ Real-time event streaming with sub-second latency&#xa;✓ Kafka-compatible message broker (Redpanda) at :9092&#xa;✓ Consumer group with auto-commit and offset tracking&#xa;✓ 3-step transformation: Validate → Enrich (high_value flag for $1000+) → Filter&#xa;✓ Fault-tolerant: 3-retry mechanism for database operations&#xa;✓ Real-time aggregation on product_sales_summary table&#xa;✓ Analytics queries exported to CSV files for visualization&#xa;✓ Color coding: Yellow=Source, Green=Producer, Purple=Broker, Orange=Consumer, Green=Transform, Purple=DB, Blue=Analytics" style="rounded=0;fillColor=#F5F5F5;strokeColor=#757575;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=8;align=left;padding=5;spacing=2;" vertex="1" parent="1">
